.SH NAME
zerocopy-audit-cli \- Automated Infrastructure Auditor for ZeroCopy Systems
.SH SYNOPSIS
zerocopy-audit-cli [options]
.SH DESCRIPTION
zerocopy-audit-cli runs a suite of compliance and performance checks against local environment, AWS infrastructure, and Kubernetes clusters. It is designed for high-frequency trading infrastructure verification.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-json\fR
Output results in JSON format for CI/CD integration.
.TP
\fB\-\-output\fR <FILE>
Write report to specified file path.
.TP
\fB\-\-quiet\fR
Minimize output (only errors).
.TP
\fB\-\-sim\fR
Simulate checks (useful for dev/test without AWS credentials).
.TP
\fB\-\-verify\-contract\fR
Verify audit results against the AuditRegistry smart contract on Sepolia.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Run full audit and save to report.txt:
.B zerocopy-audit-cli --output report.txt
.TP
Run in CI mode (simulated, json):
.B zerocopy-audit-cli --sim --json
